## Init Project

```sh
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate.bat

python.exe -m pip install --upgrade pip

pip install "fastapi[standard]" uvicorn

python backend/fastapi/main.py

cd backend/fastapi
uvicorn main:app --port 8000

pip freeze > requirements.txt
```

## Docker Build and Run

```sh
cd backend/fastapi

# build image: single stage
docker build -t fastapi:single -f Dockerfile .
# run
docker run --rm -d --name fastapi-single -p 8000:8000 fastapi:single

# build image: multiple stage
docker build -t fastapi:multiple  -f Dockerfile.multiple .
# run
docker run --rm -d --name fastapi-multiple -p 8000:8000 fastapi:multiple
```

## Image Diff

```sh
docker images fastapi
# REPOSITORY   TAG        IMAGE ID       CREATED          SIZE
# fastapi      multiple   db644a57807e   41 minutes ago   231MB
# fastapi      single     ca666af50d11   44 minutes ago   247MB
```

